      <title>Apple Store 零售店与 CWA 合作组建 104 名员工工会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/apple-store-working-with-cwa-to-unionize-104-employees-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州肖特山高档小镇的一家苹果零售店已请愿成立工会，这是在沉寂一年后首次发起此类行动。以美国通信工人协会为代表的工作人员周一向国家劳工关系委员会提交了请愿书。马克·古尔曼报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/apple-store-working-with-cwa-to-unionize-104-employees-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 20:20:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
