    <item>
      <title>华尔街从银行盈利中关注什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/what-wall-street-is-watching-for-from-bank-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者正在为摩根大通、美国银行和花旗周五公布的美国主要银行第一季度收益做准备。彭博社的索纳利·巴萨克 (Sonali Basak) 对三大值得关注的关键事项有更多的看法。投资者最感兴趣的是净利息收入。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/what-wall-street-is-watching-for-from-bank-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 20:06:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员对冲通胀，鲍威尔的软着陆梦想面临危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/powell-s-soft-landing-dream-in-danger-as-traders-hedge-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通胀尚未释放对市场的控制的迹象已经酝酿了数周。在周三高于预期的消费者价格指数导致股票和债券下跌后，现在他们正沸腾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/powell-s-soft-landing-dream-in-danger-as-traders-hedge-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀可能推迟降息，金价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在关键通胀报告连续第三个月超过预期后，金价下跌，表明持续的价格压力可能会将美联储的降息推迟到今年晚些时候。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 01:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔 500 指数受到美联储转向重新思考和战争恐慌的打击：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在另一份热门通胀报告暗示美联储今年不会急于降息后，华尔街交易员导致股票和债券下跌。随着地缘政治紧张局势再度浮现，油价攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:14:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
